{"tid":772541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB男神余德丞踢波昏迷 留醫ICU情況危殆","createTime":"2018-08-09T00:16:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T00:17:28.000Z","uid":36494,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ec4bff091d1c5eb22e2edc4081c8c76164e185f0","tid":772541,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T00:16:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180809&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58540373\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180809%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58540373&d=y88yNcyOA9CY7UWZlSDzDv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=b439e1f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180809%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58540373&h=0d46baf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180809&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58540373</a><br />\n<br />\n【男神昏迷●不斷更新】TVB男神余德丞踢波昏迷 留醫ICU情況危殆"},{"pid":"8103c3d0e48db60e53e111716c975b8881d1ad0b","tid":772541,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T00:17:28.000Z","msg":"近期人氣急升，被稱為新一代男神的無綫電視藝員余德丞（Dickson），昨晚在西營盤中山紀念公園球場踢波，疑身體不適在場外一張長椅休息，其間突然暈倒昏迷送院，至凌晨仍在深切治療部搶救，大批親友在醫院等候，為他祈禱祝福。<br />\n<br />\n現場是中山紀念公園球場，事發昨晚10時許，余德丞與朋友在球場踢波，其間感不適到場外一張長椅休息，未許即暈倒。其時27歲姓黃波友見狀，連忙報警。余其後由救護車送往瑪麗醫院搶救。"}]}